[LITA LAUGHING]

31:02.200 --> 31:05.170
DAPHNE: Looks like Lita's little
press conference was good for business.

31:05.320 --> 31:07.482
BOYS [IN UNISON]:
Aah! Vampire!

31:08.040 --> 31:09.166
Where? Where?

31:09.800 --> 31:10.881
[GROWLING]

31:11.040 --> 31:12.246
[RATTLING]

31:12.400 --> 31:13.401
[LAUGHS]

31:13.560 --> 31:16.040
Fred, don't tell me
you're buying into the hype.

31:16.200 --> 31:17.201
[CHUCKLES]

31:17.360 --> 31:19.010
Of course not.

31:19.160 --> 31:20.844
Want a bite of this garlic pizza?

31:21.000 --> 31:23.970
It has magical protective powers.

31:25.000 --> 31:26.650
[LAUGHING]

31:26.800 --> 31:30.646
Having a vampire on the loose is the best
thing that's ever happened to this festival.

31:30.800 --> 31:32.848
Hasn't boosted my book sales.

31:34.760 --> 31:38.162
- It just did.
- Why, thank you, Lita.

31:38.320 --> 31:39.526
You want it signed?

31:39.680 --> 31:41.648
Sure, make it out to "receptacle."

31:42.600 --> 31:43.886
Trash receptacle.

31:44.640 --> 31:46.449
- Huh?
- Ha-ha-ha!

31:48.280 --> 31:49.327
SHAGGY:
Hey!

31:49.480 --> 31:53.166
It's getting so you can't find a safe place
to hide anywhere.

31:53.320 --> 31:58.121
Vampires are all around us, people.
Now, keep alert.

31:58.280 --> 32:01.170
You hear that, Scoob?
Let's move, move, move.

32:01.320 --> 32:04.244
Hey, Poubelle,
I told you to get off the property.

32:04.400 --> 32:06.562
You're scaring away the customers.

32:06.720 --> 32:10.247
<i>I'm here with Jesper Poubelle from the
Society for Moral and Wholesome Living.</i>

32:10.400 --> 32:13.483
<i>Jesper, how can people slay safe
from vampire attacks?</i>

32:13.640 --> 32:19.044
<i>They can join in our crusade of moral
